{
  "note": "Human-like avatar mix so the player list looks hand-picked, not bot-generated. (1) ~noAvatarChance of users get NO avatar (null -> initial fallback), like real people who never set one. (2) peopleShare of the rest get a REAL-PERSON PHOTO from a small FINITE set (randomuser.me + pravatar.cc), so photos naturally OVERLAP between users, just like real people reusing common stock images. (3) the remainder get a unique illustrated avatar (DiceBear SVG / RoboHash) seeded by their id. Photo {n} = a random index inside the set's range; illustrated {seed} = the user's unique id. All sources are free, no key, direct image URLs. Verified 200 image/jpeg on 2026-06-16.",
  "noAvatarChance": 0.15,
  "peopleShare": 0.6,
  "people": [
    { "url": "https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/{n}.jpg", "from": 0, "count": 100 },
    { "url": "https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/{n}.jpg", "from": 0, "count": 100 },
    { "url": "https://i.pravatar.cc/300?img={n}", "from": 1, "count": 70 }
  ],
  "illustrated": [
    "https://api.dicebear.com/9.x/adventurer/svg?seed={seed}",
    "https://api.dicebear.com/9.x/adventurer-neutral/svg?seed={seed}",
